name: NeiroWifHat
description: NeiroWifHat (NEIROH) is a meme-based cryptocurrency inspired by the popular “Doge” brand. It introduces a playful character known as the “sister of Doge,” combining humor, pop culture references, and a lighthearted, community-driven approach. NEIROH aims to create a fun and engaging environment for crypto enthusiasts, focusing on the growing interest in meme coins while providing a speculative asset for investors in the space.
